cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use Glite ARF in your research, please cite it as below."
title: "Glite Autonomous Research Framework (Glite ARF)"
abstract: >-
  Glite ARF is a file-based, verification-first framework for running
  AI-driven research projects. Each task runs in isolation, every artifact
  follows a versioned specification, every step is logged, and verificator
  scripts block commits that violate structure. Completed tasks are frozen
  so later work can build on them without breaking them.
